| Target job verified | ✅ Owner: `test-developer`, Environment: `test`, Managed-by: `manual-test` |
| Production job preserved | ✅ `data-sync-job-v2-active` still Running (owner: `platform-team`) |
| Job deleted | ✅ `data-sync-job` returns NotFound |
| Pod deleted | ✅ `data-sync-job-pod` removed |
| Shared PVC preserved | ✅ `data-sync-storage` intact (shared by api-service, reporting-service) |
| Shared Secret preserved | ✅ `db-credentials` intact (shared by api-service, worker-service) |

The NodeDiskPressure alert on worker-node-03 has been resolved by removing the stray test job that was generating excessive log output and leaving a stuck pod consuming ephemeral storage.
